  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n68/mode/1up">65</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n68/mode/1up">65</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. mēṟcollappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiyuḷ, mutaṟkaṭpeyareṉṟu kūṟappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiyāvatu peyar tōṉṟiya tuṇaiyāy niṟkunilaimaiyām. e - ṟu.</p>
<p>peyar tōṉṟiya tuṇaiyāy niṟkunilaimaiyāvatu urupum viḷiyumēlātu piṟitoṉṟaṉoṭu tokātu niṟkunilaimai. eṉavē, urupum viḷiyumēṟṟum piṟitoṉṟaṉoṭu tokkum niṉṟa peyar eḻuvāyvēṟṟumaiyākā teṉṟavāṟām.</p>
<p>u-m. ā, avaṉ eṉa varum.	(4)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
